reviewText: I love this series but sad to say they are no longer producing these DVD for kids!  I bought them all once I found out...they are GREAT and all are based on a story out of the bible!  My grandkids love these DVD's - I don't understand how they were not a big HIT!  If they are still available I highly recommend you buying these.

I had been looking for more of the Roach Approach and/or Bug Rangers dvds when I found these.  These dvds teach biblical principles through the biblical stories they present.  Children and adults alike will enjoy the colors and animation and imagination used in this presentation. I received the dvd in a timely fashion, actually earlier than I had expected.  The product came undamaged, with the packaging intack.
